FBIS3-58357 "drweu008_n_94003" FBIS-WEU-94-008 Document Type:Daily Report 12 Jan 1994 NORDIC COUNTRIES Sweden Foreign Minister Critical of Russia's Threat to Latvia LD1201113794 Helsinki Suomen Yleisradio Network in Finnish 1100 GMT 12 Jan 94 LD1201113794 Helsinki Suomen Yleisradio Network Language: Finnish Article Type:BFN [Text] Swedish Foreign Minister Margaretha Af Ugglas has severely criticized Russia for threatening Latvia. Last Monday [10 January], Russia placed units of its border troops on alert after two Russian generals were arrested in Latvia. According to the Swedish foreign minister, such actions violate the principles of the CSCE, and are unacceptable.
